   <description>
      <short>
         <en><![CDATA[Fork of the Data Injection plugin with GLPI 11 custom-asset support and XLSX imports.]]></en>
      </short>
      <long>
         <en><![CDATA[Imports CSV and XLSX files into GLPI tables. Adds full support for GLPI 11 custom assets (the glpi_assets_assets table) including the per-definition JSON custom_fields column, on top of the original plugin's coverage of standard inventory, management and configuration data.]]></en>
      </long>
